            "value": "<p>This black pearl sparkles with light. The resonant power allows you to cast sending once per day.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">R</span>&nbsp;envision;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger</strong>&nbsp;you are targeted by a mental effect;&nbsp;<strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;You receive a +4 status bonus to your saving throw against the triggering effect. Whether or not your save is successful, the aeon stone attempts a counteract check at +30 to immediately reflect a copy of the effect back at the originator, targeting it using the creatureâ€™s own relevant statistics but controlling the effect as if you had cast it.&nbsp;<br>Every time you activate this aeon stone, attempt a DC 5 flat check. On a failure, the stone shatters and loses its magical properties forever.</p>",
